<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE05FFC5FC98FCAEFB80562B" box="[895,1066,867,884]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Cotoneaster insignis</emphasis>
Pojark.
</taxonomicName>
leaves and fruits outline (
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE05FFC5FAA2FCAEFAF8562B" bold="true" box="[1349,1362,867,884]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">A</emphasis>
) and close up (
