). Collection number: 
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE05FFC5FBE0FCB4FABE56D5" box="[1031,1300,889,906]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Attar, Raei Niaki &amp; Zamani 37454</emphasis>
