<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE05FFC5FF62FB58FF6D51F2" blockId="12.[131,776,1173,1358]" box="[133,199,1173,1199]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">NOTE</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE05FFC5FF63FB79FDFA5011" blockId="12.[131,776,1173,1358]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">
This species has been reported from 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE05FFC5FDF2FB78FDE95190" box="[533,579,1205,1231]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
without mention of the locality (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE05FFC5FEC0FB19FE0B51B1" author="RIEDL H." box="[295,417,1236,1262]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" pagination="13 - 26" refId="ref5495" refString="RIEDL H. 1969. - Cotoneaster Medik., in RECHINGER K. H. (ed.), Flora Iranica. Akademische Druck und Verlagsanstalt, Graz 66: 13 - 26." type="journal article" year="1969">Riedl 1969</bibRefCitation>
). So, this species was not verified as a native species for 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE05FFC5FE64FB38FE1B5050" box="[387,433,1269,1295]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE05FFC5FE22FB39FD295051" author="KHATAMSAZ M." box="[453,643,1268,1294]" pageId="12" pageNumber="151" pagination="209 - 239" refId="ref4690" refString="KHATAMSAZ M. 1992. - Cotoneaster Medik., in ASSADI M. (ed.), Flora of Iran. Research institute of forests and rangelands publication, Tehran 6: 209 - 239 [in Persian]." type="journal article" year="1992">Khatamsaz 1992</bibRefCitation>
). However, this species was found from west 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE05FFC5FE11FAD8FD8E5070" box="[502,548,1301,1327]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="151">Iran</collectingCountry>
and is introduced as a new record based on the collected data.
</paragraph>
